although it is possible to use &quot;Zero Cross&quot; and &quot;Use Cue List&quot; at the
same time, it is unnecessary, since I had already zero-crossed the cue
ranges in Audition.

(Just a hint...)

But please, I don&#39;t wanna keep anyone from playing and experimenting.
Not seldom users discover potentialities of an application even the
developer never knew of... :)

Stefan

